alse}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ana Wagener","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"阿娜·阿尔瓦雷斯·瓦格纳（生于1962年）是西班牙女演员","name":"阿娜·瓦格纳","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"阿娜·阿爾瓦雷斯·瓦格納（生於 1962 年）是西班牙女演員","name":"阿娜·瓦格納","primary":false}}]}},"person_37403_translations":{"at":1773688722763,"data":{"id":37403,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"A South African born New Yorker with over three decades of versatile, award winning performances in popular, world-wide theatrically released studio & independent films, prime-time & cable television & New York theater. After small speaking roles opposite Russell Crowe in Ron Howard's A Beautiful Mind (2001) & David Chase's The Sopranos (1999) as Gaetano; his breakthrough lead role came in 2005 on Law & Order: Special Victims Unit (1999) directed by Oscar winner Juan José Campanella. Starring opposite Mariska Hargitay, Chris Meloni, & Bradley Cooper as the chilling yet engaging fundamentalist Milan Zergin. Also, a coveted recurring role on Ugly Betty (2006), becoming South Africa's first male SAG Award Nominee (Ensemble Comedy Performance). Followed by significant supporting roles in the studio films My Super Ex-Girlfriend (2006) opposite Eddie Izzard, Luke Wilson, & Uma Thurman directed by Ivan Reitman for Twentieth Century Fox . An ensemble lead in Sony's Starship Troopers 3: Marauder (2008) produced by David Lancaster, a supporting role in Pure Flix's What If... (2010), & supporting lead in the Lionsgate family film Army Dog (2016) .","name":"Stelio Savante","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"一位出生于南非的纽约人，在流行的、全球影院发行的工作室和独立电影、黄金时段和有线电视以及纽约剧院中拥有超过三十年的多才多艺、屡获殊荣的表演。在罗恩·霍华德（Ron Howard）的《美丽心灵》（A Beautiful Mind，2001年）和大卫·蔡斯（David Chase）的《黑道家族》（The Sopranos，1999年）中与罗素·克劳（Russell Crowe）演对手戏后，饰演加埃塔诺（Gaetano）;2005年，他在奥斯卡奖得主胡安·何塞·坎帕内拉（Juan José Campanella）执导的《法律与秩序：特殊受害者》（Law & Order： Special Victims Unit，1999）中担任突破性的主角。与玛丽斯卡·哈吉泰、克里斯·梅洛尼和布拉德利·库珀演对手戏，饰演令人不寒而栗但引人入胜的原教旨主义者米兰·泽尔金。此外，在《丑陋的贝蒂》（2006 年）中，她经常出演令人垂涎的角色，成为南非第一位男性 SAG 奖提名人（合奏喜剧表演）。随后在工作室电影《我的超级前女友》（2006）中扮演重要配角，与埃迪·伊扎德、卢克·威尔逊和乌玛·瑟曼对戏，由伊万·雷特曼为二十世纪福克斯执导。大卫·兰开斯特（David Lancaster）制作的索尼《星际战队3：掠夺者》（2008）中的合奏主角，在Pure Flix的《如果...（2010年），并在狮门影业家庭电影《军犬》（2016年）中担任配角。","name":"斯泰利奥·萨万特","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Стелио Саванте","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"一位出生於南非的紐約人，在流行的、全球影院發行的工作室和獨立電影、黃金時段和有線電視以及紐約劇院中擁有超過三十年的多才多藝、屢獲殊榮的表演。在羅恩·霍華德（Ron Howard）的《有你終生美麗》（A Beautiful Mind，2001 年）和大衞·蔡斯（David Chase）的《黑道家族》（The Sopranos，1999 年）中與羅素·克勞（Russell Crowe）演對手戲後，飾演加埃塔諾（Gaetano）; 2005 年，他在奧斯卡獎得主胡安·何塞·坎帕內拉（Juan José Campanella）執導的《法律與秩序：特殊受害者》（Law & Order： Special Victims Unit，1999）中擔任突破性的主角。與瑪麗斯卡·哈吉泰、克里斯·梅洛尼和布拉德利·庫珀演對手戲，飾演令人不寒而栗但引人入勝的原教旨主義者米蘭·澤爾金。此外，在《醜陋的貝蒂》（2006 年）中，她經常出演令人垂涎的角色，成為南非第一位男性 SAG 獎提名人（合奏喜劇表演）。隨後在工作室電影《我的超人女友》（2006）中扮演重要配角，與埃迪·伊紮德、盧克·威爾遜和烏瑪·瑟曼對戲，由伊萬·雷特曼為二十世紀福克斯執導。大衞·蘭開斯特（David Lancaster）製作的索尼《星際戰隊 3：掠奪者》（2008）中的合奏主角，在 Pure Flix 的《如果. . . （2010 年），並在獅門影業家庭電影《軍犬》（2016 年）中擔任配角。","name":"斯泰利奧·薩萬特","primary":false}}]}},"person_3434818_translations":{"at":1773688725147,"data":{"id":3434818,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Qian Chen (chēn) is a female voice actor from China. Member of new generation of 729 Sound Factory. A member of the Chinese group Coedna and also in the original idol project 